Title: Boom Bait
Description:
There. I've plastered your bird guts over my explosives.

I call 'em Gut Bombs, patent pending.

Since you made friends with these fellas, how about you do the honors?

Just light the fuse and throw 'em down by the shoreline!
ObjectivesText: Use the Gut Bombs at Murky Bank and collect 5 Exploded Slickies.
